snippet.title: Kokoa: The Paperverse Gameplay Trailer!
snippet.description:
Kokoa is a Nintendo inspired RPG, help Kokoa and Dawn defeat a Magician with Malicious court! A demo for Kokoa will be made available on Steam and Itch.io in the future!

This trailer was made originally for @Paperverse 's Paperverse Direct 2024!
